verbose_text: The Tg [ET (krt4 : EGFP) sqet20] line marks interneuromast cells and highlights the equatorial areas (XREF_FIG C, supplementary material Fig. S1), whereas the red-fluorescent Tg [Alpl : mCherry] is expressed homogeneously in the peripheral cells of the neuromast and in interneuromast cells (XREF_FIG C, supplementary material Fig. S1).
